'''1700年卡斯凯迪亚地震'''是指1700年发生在[[卡斯凯迪亚隱沒帶|卡斯凯迪亚隱沒帶]]的一场[[矩震級|矩震級]]為8.7到9.2的[[大型逆衝區地震|大型逆衝區地震]]（Megathrust earthquake）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://soundwaves.usgs.gov/2007/10/outreach3.html |title=USGS Scientist Shows Evidence for 300-Year-Old Tsunami to Participants in International Tsunami Training Institute |accessdate=2008-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080511222845/http://soundwaves.usgs.gov/2007/10/outreach3.html |archivedate=2008-05-11 }}</ref>。这场[[地震|地震]]源于[[太平洋|太平洋]]下的[[胡安·德富卡板块|胡安·德富卡板块]]，该板块起于[[加拿大|加拿大]]西南部[[不列颠哥伦比亚|不列颠哥伦比亚]]的[[溫哥華島|溫哥華島]]中部，沿著[[太平洋西北地区|太平洋西北地区]]海岸伸展。这场地震也造成的断层长度约为1,000公里，平均落差约20公尺。

这场地震也還造成了袭击日本沿岸的巨大[[海啸|海啸]]<ref name=japan>{{cite web |url=http://pubs.usgs.gov/pp/pp1707/pp1707.pdf |title=The Orphan Tsunami of 1700—Japanese Clues to a Parent Earthquake in North America |accessdate=2008-05-06 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002712/https://pubs.usgs.gov/pp/pp1707/pp1707.pdf |dead-url=no }} USGS Professional Paper 1707</ref>，同时也很有可能是俄勒冈州著名地质结构{{le|众神之桥|Bridge of the Gods (land bridge)}}的原因<ref name=bonneville>{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/regional/pacnw/paleo/greateq/20020515.html |title=Possible tie to the Bonneville Slide |accessdate=2008-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081024134333/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/regional/pacnw/paleo/greateq/20020515.php |archivedate=2008-10-24 }} USGS</ref>。

